{"pin":"AB10769","subcodes":[{"code":"AB10769","anchor":"","first_line":"O my Lord, my Beloved, my Desire! Befriend me in my loneliness and accompany me in my exile","first_line_orig":"ربی و محبوبی و مقصودی آنسنی فی وحدتی و رافقنی فی غربتی و اکشف کربتی و هیمنی  ","language":"Ara","word_count":"70","subjects":"@prayer for nearness to God, @detachment; severance; renunciation; patience","full_text_parts":["O my Lord, my Beloved, my Desire! Befriend me in my loneliness and accompany me in my exile. Remove my sorrow. Cause me to be devoted to Thy beauty. Withdraw me from all else save Thee. Attract me through Thy fragrances of holiness. Cause me to be associated in Thy Kingdom with those who are severed from all else save Thee, who long to serve Thy sacred threshold and who stand to work in Thy Cause. Enable me to be one of Thy maidservants who have attained to Thy good pleasure. Verily, Thou art the Gracious, the Generous."],"translations":[{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"kj","lang_name":"Oshikwanyama"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"language":"mr","lang_name":"Marathi"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"az",